sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Watch as Smartwatch
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant Server as Backend Server

    User->>App: Open Watch-App
    App->>Server: Request smartwatch integration
    Server-->>App: Send integration details
    App->>Watch: Send integration details
    Watch-->>User: Display integration confirmation
    User->>Watch: Start using features
    Watch->>Server: Sync data
    Server-->>Watch: Send updated data
    Watch-->>User: Display updated information